{"title":"攀登","authors":["峭石"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":7,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前又崛起一座山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直楞楞地插向天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急流在山脚咆哮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云潮在山腰翻腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巉岩上缠绕着藤葛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石缝里倒挂着青松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左右瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有攀缘的阶梯？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上下寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何处是前进的路径？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗迎风飞卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军号仰天长鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政委扬臂高呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同电闪雷轰："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进，阶级的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进，革命的英雄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊罢仰起头来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个飞身先登。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，你听这雄壮的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不就是党的号召；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，你看这坚强的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它就是威严的命令！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一霎时千军万马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气势如海潮奔涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶上红星闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸膛里烈火熊熊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手抓着细小的岩缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踩着古老的葛藤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任荆棘刺破皮肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任鲜血把苔藓染红……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看战士如支支飞箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射向那巍巍的高峰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，在漫长的征途上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有过多少次攀登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从秋雨秋风的井冈山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到春风春雨的珠穆朗玛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士迈着豪壮的步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过无数险峻的山峰——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨石光滑脚难踩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巉岩棱棱如刀锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万年洪荒无人走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶狼嗥叫虎豹凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林深草密不见天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半山积雪半山冰……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，我们是山的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最爱走这样的路程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰险，唯有艰险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能显示我们的性格；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难，唯有困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才觉得乐趣无穷——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清山泉濯脚板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密林深处架帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆堆篝火驱寒夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵暴雨洗征尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野味拌着鲜蘑煮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞罢干粮嚼冰凌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风雷唱战歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花摇珠露伴我行……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少山，多少岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山岭岭有行踪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少岭，多少山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岭岭山山留歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当攀上一座峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又获得了一个新的胜利；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当登上一座岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又行进到一个新的里程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我们攀登过的每座峰啊每座岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又都是一个新起点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又都使我们开始了新的战斗，新的长征！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀一峰，又一峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀一岭，又一岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峰连岭来岭连峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峰峰岭岭不消停——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋千丈飞瀑溅珠玉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋野菊金黄山茶红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋枝头黄鹂缠绵调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋林中孔雀闹彩翎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋笋嫩鱼鲜滋味美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋风柔日暖彩云轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋庆功筵上胜利酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留恋和平年月鼓乐声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士心在斗争里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄志在最高峰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的车轮要旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的骏马要飞腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不怕六月炎阳如烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不怕雪封山崖三尺冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不怕云低风紧暴雨狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不怕电闪雷鸣鬼神惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不怕虎狼当道舞牙爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱不怕毒蛇拦路瞪眼睛……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前险关千万道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一道一道要踏平；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上高峰有多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一座一座要攀登！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的身姿——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羽翼飞展的雄鹰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的气概——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横贯天宇的长虹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有天一样宽阔的胸襟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有海一样澎湃的豪情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说攀缘无阶梯？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我们双手上一道金梯接天架；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说眼前无道路？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我们双脚下一条大道正诞生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远攀登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这才是辉煌灿烂的人生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我们的全部力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我们的整个生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终会有这么一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要登上人类历史的顶峰——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！无限风光在险峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高歌一曲全球红！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}